Agriculture Cabinet Secretary, Mwangi Kiunjuri is a troubled man, with the happenings in his ministry seemingly drawing the wrath of the head of state Uhuru Kenyatta. Analysts  say that with the President is keen on implementing the big four agenda, but frustrated with the treatment that farmers are getting from departments under the ministry, including the NCPB and Wanton graft , Kiunjuri might continue taking the heat for a long time. 